  <atom:content type="xhtml">
    <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
      <p>This plugin includes an authentication module (must be activated in web.config) and a couple widgets to allow logging into the site via <a href="http://openid.net">OpenID</a>.</p>
      <p>
        <strong style="#a90000">Update </strong> Now the web.config file gets updated automatically during setup.
      </p>
      <h3>Web.config Settings</h3>
      <h4>IE7</h4>
      <p>If installing manually, add the following line to the &lt;system.webServer&gt; &lt;modules&gt; section:</p>
      <code>
        &lt;add name="OpenIdAuthenticationModule" type="AtomSite.Plugins.OpenIdPlugin.OpenIdAuthenticationModule, AtomSite.Plugins.OpenIdPlugin"/&gt;
      </code>
    </div>
  </atom:content>
